   <conbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">There are three ways to connect to the command
line interface (CLI):<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <xref href="#./Local-CLI-via-NMC"
                              scope="local"
                              type="section"
                              class="- topic/xref ">Local access via the network management card</xref>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <xref href="#./Local-CLI-via-SST"
                              scope="local"
                              type="section"
                              class="- topic/xref ">Local access via the smart slot translator</xref>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <xref href="#./Remote-CLI-via-NMC"
                              scope="local"
                              type="section"
                              class="- topic/xref ">Remote access</xref>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
            </p>
            <note platform="SDC" class="- topic/note ">SDC systems uses the smart slot translator
but the port cannot be accessed, since the card is not placed in the
low voltage section.</note>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section id="Local-CLI-via-NMC" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Connect and Configure Local
Access to the CLI via the NMC</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure you have a serial port on the local computer. Disable
any services that uses that port.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Connect the serial cable (Reality part number: 940-0299) to the
serial port on the computer and the serial configuration port on the
NMC.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Start a terminal emulator and configure the connected serial
port on to:<table class="- topic/table ">
                           <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                              <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                              <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                              <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Name</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Value</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                              </thead>
                              <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Baud rate</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">9600 bps</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Data</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">8 bit</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Parity</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">None</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Stop</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">1 bit</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Flow control</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">None</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                              </tbody>
                           </tgroup>
                        </table>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol>. When prompted
enter the user name and password to login to the CLI.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">For more information about the setting options in the CLI see, <xref href="NMC_Overview_of_the_Command_Line_Interface_CPT_0000354489.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/> and <xref href="NMC_Command_Line_Interface_Commands_and_How_to_Configure_CPT_0000354488.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>. For information on
how to change the IP address see <xref href="Configure_from_the_CLI_CPT_0000354856.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">To log out from the CLI type <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">exit</codeph> or <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">quit</codeph> and press <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol>.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section id="Local-CLI-via-SST" platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Connect
and Configure Local Access to the CLI via the Smart Slot Translator</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure you have a serial port on the local computer. Disable
any services that uses that port.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Connect a serial DB-9 cable to the serial port on the computer
and the serial monitoring port <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">J6</b> on the smart slot translator.</p>
                     <table class="- topic/table ">
                        <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                           <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <colspec colname="col3" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                              <row class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p class="- topic/p ">Male Cable End</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p class="- topic/p ">Female Cable
End</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p class="- topic/p ">Description</p>
                                 </entry>
                              </row>
                           </thead>
                           <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                              <row class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">1</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">3</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">TXD</p>
                                 </entry>
                              </row>
                              <row class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">2</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">2</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">RXD</p>
                                 </entry>
                              </row>
                              <row class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">9</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">5</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">GND</p>
                                 </entry>
                              </row>
                              <row class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">–</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p class="- topic/p ">1 connected to 4</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">DCD – DRT</p>
                                 </entry>
                              </row>
                              <row class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">–</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p class="- topic/p ">7 connected to 8</p>
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                    <p class="- topic/p ">shield</p>
                                 </entry>
                              </row>
                           </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                     </table>
                     <note class="- topic/note ">Do not connect or use other pins!</note>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Start a terminal emulator and configure the connected serial
port on to:<table class="- topic/table ">
                           <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                              <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                              <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                              <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Name</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Value</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                              </thead>
                              <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Baud rate</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">2400 bps</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Data</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">8 bit</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Parity</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">None</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Stop</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">1 bit</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                                 <row class="- topic/row ">
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">Flow control</p>
                                    </entry>
                                    <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                       <p class="- topic/p ">None</p>
                                    </entry>
                                 </row>
                              </tbody>
                           </tgroup>
                        </table>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol>. When prompted
enter the user name and password to login to the CLI.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">For more information about the setting options in the CLI see, <xref href="NMC_Overview_of_the_Command_Line_Interface_CPT_0000354489.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/> and <xref href="NMC_Command_Line_Interface_Commands_and_How_to_Configure_CPT_0000354488.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>. For information on
how to change the IP address see <xref href="Configure_from_the_CLI_CPT_0000354856.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">To log out from the CLI type <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">exit</codeph> or <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">quit</codeph> and press <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol>.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section id="Remote-CLI-via-NMC" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Connect and Configure Remote
Access to the CLI</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">To access the CLI remotely
an IP address or a DNS name must be configured for the NMC card, see <xref href="How_to_Define_an_IP_address_for_the_NMC_CPT_0000355042.dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="concept"
                     class="- topic/xref "/>. The
remote access can use Telnet for basic access or SSH for secure encrypted
access.</p>
            <note class="- topic/note ">Without encryption the user name, password and data
are transmitted as plain text. Plain text can be read by someone that
monitors the network traffic.</note>
            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Start a terminal emulator from a computer on the same sub network
as the NMC.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">In the command line type <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">telnet xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx</codeph> where <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx</codeph> is the IPv4
address of the NMC.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Enter your user name and press <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Enter your password and press <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol>.<note class="- topic/note ">For access with SSH, type <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">ssh</codeph> instead of <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">telnet</codeph> in the command
line if configured.</note>
                        <note class="- topic/note ">If configured, the DNS or IPv6 name
can be used instead of the IPv4 address of the NMC.</note>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
